	<clause id="_operation_of_the_jctlm" obligation="normative"><title>Operation of the JCTLM</title><p id="_3ca29e71-5d22-4c65-bffd-5aefd2597c9d">The operation of the JCTLM is overseen by its Executive Committee being the impartial final decision making organ, only accountable to the Executive Committee member organizations.</p>
	<clause id="scls_7-1" obligation="normative"><p id="_ea67b16f-ab73-4f8d-a9c4-5fc6c4771823">JCTLM is led by the Executive Committee according to a set of procedures that govern the activities of this committee. These procedures are:</p>
